text: My children attended their summer camp and it was fabulous. The coaches were attentive and they were very patient with my children. Hope to join again, thumbs up guys

We went for the June holiday camp at west coast. For the first 3 days we were assigned very young trainers. Trainers lack experience and there was little structure to the camp. Gears were in bad condition, overstretched and loose and half of them couldn't stay on and kept slipping. An experienced trainer joined on the last day but only focused on the younger kids. End up the children failed to learn the right techniques even after 2.5hrs x 4 days.
Very pleasant experience. We went for holidays camp at the stadium and the coach ratio was excellent. Happy that my children enjoyed it
Wonderful coaches! Joined their class at stadium after the skate camp and it is awesome.
Thank you coaches for the wonderful post exam programmes!
